splendid perch
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:Brightly coloured fish found in southern Australian and northern and central NZ waters, also known as Allport's perch.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:Allport's perch
Pronunciation:
Notes: <i>Callanthias allporti</i> aka Allport's perch
Citations
